      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ENOLA (9) has finished fourth in her last two outings at Menangle, leading at her latest appearance and sticking on well to be beaten 4 metres. May need luck at some stage extracting from the inside of the second row but she is up to winning this if things go her way. CONCILIATE (8) comes through the same Menangle race as ENOLA and was just behind her. The driver has some work to do from this wide starting position but she strikes at 50 per cent at this circuit and distance so can win with her A-game. LINE OF COURAGE (2) eases back in grade on the last attempt and was racing consistently prior. Draws to be competitive. JETASI NZ (7) draws wide but has claims off a Penrith win two back.",
